value.0: The Silver Dragons serve and protect the people, acting as the first line of defense against would-be villains and criminals.
This is a settlement guard insignia for the guard templates.

The Order Silver Dragon Knights are an elite force of warriors that serve the Crown, often acting directly on the orders of the Lord Commander or Regent. They are law keepers and defenders of the innocent, always serving the ideals of the Triad and Bahamut above all else.
